@startuml
title 支付回调流程（含幂等 + 库存扣减）

actor "支付网关\n(支付宝/微信)" as paygw
participant "payment-core" as payment
participant "order-core" as order
participant "workflow-service\n(Saga Orchestrator)" as wf
participant "inventory-service" as inv
participant "logistics-service" as logistics
queue "RocketMQ" as mq
participant "user-center" as uc
note left of uc: 双协议：MQ（异步事件）\n+ Dubbo/mTLS（同步RPC）
participant "通知服务" as notify

' ADR-020 CreateOrderSagaDefinition Step 3 (chargePayment) 由 payment-service
' 在接收支付回调时调用三方网关执行；Step 4 (confirmOrder) 映射为 order.paySuccess。
' 本图展示回调触发后的编排。详见 saga-orchestration.puml "支付成功 Saga"。

== 支付回调 ==
paygw -> payment: POST 异步回调 (signature + transaction_id)
activate payment
payment -> payment: 验签 (RSA256)
payment -> payment: 幂等校验 (payment_transaction_id 唯一索引)

alt 已处理过的回调（幂等）
    payment --> paygw: HTTP 200 (已处理，忽略)
else 首次回调
    payment -> order: 支付成功通知 (Dubbo: paySuccess)
    activate order
    order -> order: 状态机 PENDING_PAY → PAID
    order -> order: 更新实际支付金额 + 支付时间
    order --> payment: 成功
    deactivate order

    payment -> wf: 触发支付成功Saga编排
    activate wf

    wf -> inv: 确认扣减库存 (confirmDeduct)
    activate inv
    inv -> inv: Redis 预占转正式扣减
    inv --> wf: 成功
    deactivate inv

    wf -> logistics: 创建发货单
    activate logistics
    logistics -> logistics: 生成发货单（待发货状态）
    logistics --> wf: 成功
    deactivate logistics

    wf -> mq: 发布 OrderPaidEvent
    deactivate wf

    == 异步处理（并行）==
    par 异步同步
        mq -> es: 同步 ES 支付状态 (Canal)
        mq -> uc: 发放积分/成长值
        mq -> notify: 发送支付成功通知
    end

    payment --> paygw: HTTP 200 (处理成功)
end
deactivate payment

@enduml
